Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:39.20,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,In the 22nd century, depleted energy\Nreserves and rapid population growth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:43.47,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...have forced humans to look for\Na home in the vast reaches of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:47.74,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Each planet in the solar system, along\Nwith countless space colonies, are...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:51.35,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...connected via\Nthe Planet Network System...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:54.65,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...and humans have\Nadvanced even to Pluto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:59.55,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,100 years have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.39,0:01:03.12,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans have overcome\Nharsh living conditions...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:06.36,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...and people have adjusted to\Nlife in new environments.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:11.56,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, people's bodies\Nhave even begun to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:18.07,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one could\Nhave imagined that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:22.88,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...the day would come when they might\Nlose everything they had achieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:33.66,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,State your name and\Nidentification number.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.73,0:01:39.86,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan Tyberius.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:44.70,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,ID number\N3150-103-S.H.P.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:49.87,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan Tyberius, you are\Ndifferent from other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:55.17,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,You possess a very special power,\None I assume you're already aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:58.54,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,We are about to give you\Nthe final test to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:04.35,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...whether you have what it\Ntakes to pilot the powered suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:07.08,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...that our military has been developing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:11.78,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you requested to\Nparticipate in this project...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:15.19,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...however, I have to tell you this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:22.14,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had six people with the same\Nability you have take this test before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:26.84,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,And all have either died or gone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.98,0:02:30.51,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to stop\Nthis test, tell me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.55,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then. We will now begin the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:26.41,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Pluto became the first\Nvictim 2 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.51,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,There were no survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:33.31,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,They appeared without warning before\Nhumanity, just as they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:36.15,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...about to advance beyond the solar\Nsystem they had conquered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:40.79,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't know where they came\Nfrom, but we knew why they came.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.37,0:06:52.17,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,They would capture humans and\Nassimilate them into their bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:55.30,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...obtaining information about the\Nhuman race from their brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.75,0:07:01.65,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who were ingested became\Ncomponents for their weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:10.99,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of fear and contempt,\Nwe called them the Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:40.61,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes until shuttle descend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:44.32,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Jonathan Tyberius.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.83,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a space fleet mobile\Ninfantry unit ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:51.06,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, on my own request...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:55.27,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm heading to Ganymede,\Nthe outermost moon of Jupiter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:08:02.17,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I was trying to\Nkeep my promise to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:09.48,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,My promise to Leonard Schteinberg...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.02,0:08:21.06,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Legend of the Blue Wolves{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:26.16,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vol.1 The Seventh Man{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:55.23,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,How does that feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:59.83,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you pledge your loyalty to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:06.17,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, I do, so please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:08.30,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:11.44,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.71,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Please what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:19.25,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to tell me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.55,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.73,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:28.12,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,When you talk to your superior,\Nyou must address him as "Sir"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:34.27,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:35.96,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:38.27,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, you must entertain me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:40.17,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.28,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, now turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.68,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant, I can't hold it any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:21.69,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, are you going to climax with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:24.38,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.16,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan Tyberius...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:19.30,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:23.94,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,We are trespassing on naval\Nmanoeuvres.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.98,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remove yourself from\Nthe vicinity immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.15,0:11:28.08,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,An enforced evacuation warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.48,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:29.54,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you,\Nyou saved my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.28,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:40.55,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,If this was a real battlefield,\Nno one would save your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:49.09,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, our forces have yet\Nto achieve a successful combat test yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:53.57,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the new improved Powered\NSuit is nearing completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:57.73,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,And you are the elite, top graduates\Nfrom the military academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:01.40,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...qualified to pilot the Powered Suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:05.67,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I want you\Nto train hard as ensigns of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:09.18,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...81st mobile infantry\Nunit, 25th graduating class.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:13.82,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Those commanders who were\Npromoted in the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:17.43,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...are already at their posts,\Nso try not to cause any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.00,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:01.97,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the guy from manoeuvres...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:17.89,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.65,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:22.15,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:33.19,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are my roommate,\NEnsign Leonard Schteinberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:37.74,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Jonathan Tyberius, I have been\Nappointed here as an Ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:39.74,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the rookie lieutenant...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:44.40,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,You threw a good punch back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:45.88,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:49.94,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you were the youngest\Nmartial art champion at the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:50.95,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.46,0:14:55.45,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,So I punched someone way\Nout of my league, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:15:00.83,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was my fault, I'll never\Nmake a mistake like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.97,0:15:02.87,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.69,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,The Apocalypse don't take hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.33,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Once captured, anyone\Nwill become your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:12.61,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it is someone you love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:16.15,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...The Apocalypse will turn them into\Nyour enemy and you'll have to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:25.92,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,This training is hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.62,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you want to survive, don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.00,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Three minutes to shuttle descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:45.57,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was my mother who made\Nme choose the life of a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:51.71,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,My father died when I was little,\Nand my mother raised me by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:54.75,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,She never showed me any\Nmotherly tenderness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:58.48,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...and was very strict\Nabout my education.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:07.09,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only in academics, but she also\Nmade sure that I trained in martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:51.07,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Men have to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:55.17,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,So they can\Nprotect the ones they love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.97,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my mom used to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:03.24,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I still hear her voice inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.32,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:48.56,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you shoot the Manhead?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.49,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:54.93,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I see human faces, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:18:00.41,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think people who were\Nturned into one of them feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:01.07,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:05.01,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:08.42,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they aren't humans anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.61,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we should at\Nleast put them to rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:14.16,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...while they look human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:19.49,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot them out of their armed shell\Nand reveal their humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:22.10,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,They deserve to die\Nwith respect and dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:23.80,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,So aim well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.26,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,And make sure you kill them on the\Nspot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:31.03,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot them as your\Nenemy and one of your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:33.97,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...who have already lost their\Nhuman lives in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.63,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Ensign Tyberius.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:59.00,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Continental is calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.93,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Please report to his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.94,0:19:09.21,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Ensign Tyberius reporting, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.78,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you're having\Ntrouble at the target range.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:15.64,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:20.09,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I will earnestly try my best to\Nimprove my shooting skill, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:28.86,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I like your attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:31.97,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't understand the most\Nbasic thing about being a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:35.70,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to respond to\Nyour superiors with "Yes" or "No".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:38.73,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.23,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:42.70,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Sir, yes, sir."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.31,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:48.82,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. You're a fast learner, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.39,0:19:52.79,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your clothes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:56.05,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:57.99,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:12.50,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you pledge your loyalty to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:18.01,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Say you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.64,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, no, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.38,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:28.09,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,You object your superior's order?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:37.56,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying it as a soldier,\NI'm saying it as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.30,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me orders\Non the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:04.32,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not only the Apocalypse that\Ncan take dignity away from humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:09.63,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, it's humans who take away the\Ndignity of others for their own desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:13.56,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,How pitiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.09,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:48.23,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'd like to\Ndemonstrate Muay Thai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:50.63,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Ensign Tyberius, step up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:58.91,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you hold\Nthe record as the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:01.61,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...youngest martial arts\Nchampion in the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:03.31,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:04.61,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Very good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.66,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:08.92,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.53,0:22:11.39,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:32.91,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just started...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.08,0:22:35.61,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I will teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:42.05,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.16,0:22:44.89,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,If you pledged your loyalty\Nto me, I could stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:48.33,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never say it even if he kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:50.43,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, no, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:53.93,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told you that you could pass out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:58.43,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.01,0:23:01.94,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the\Nhell...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.50,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:10.31,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd still like to fight, I'll take his\Nplace as his roommate and fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:12.75,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.33,0:23:22.32,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to tell you, but\Nmy speciality is karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:37.48,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.12,0:23:44.85,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Continental, that bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.32,0:23:48.29,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,He did a real number on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.64,0:24:01.93,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Leonard, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:04.97,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:06.94,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.08,0:24:11.61,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll never force anyone to\Ndo what they don't want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.03,0:25:05.49,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,When I realized, I had an erection...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.82,0:25:30.69,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I would imagine myself having a\Nbeautiful body and I'd get aroused.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:34.56,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,That beautiful body\NI dreamt of having...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.47,0:25:48.57,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect body looks\Njust like Leonard's...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.75,0:25:53.31,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting aroused, but\Nnot because I was narcissistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.72,0:25:57.62,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.26,0:26:03.52,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency roll call!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.66,0:26:04.89,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency roll call!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.63,0:26:10.86,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Emergency roll call!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.64,0:26:15.59,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,We have information that a spy\Nmight have slipped into our base.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.94,0:26:18.60,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we'll perform a body cavity\Nsearch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.04,0:26:21.94,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.75,0:26:24.81,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.96,0:26:40.26,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.77,0:26:46.76,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,That is indeed the emblem of the\NApocalypse!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.00,0:26:48.87,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are the spy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.71,0:26:57.58,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you, are you the spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.91,0:26:59.75,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, no, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.08,0:27:04.52,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I guess I have to investigate\Nthis case a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.65,0:27:05.75,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.59,0:27:13.06,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're his roommate,\Nyou're also responsible for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.20,0:27:15.56,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be confined to the guardhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.26,0:28:21.86,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.21,0:29:12.24,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.02,0:29:19.65,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.82,0:29:21.42,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.30,0:29:27.63,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.36,0:30:01.76,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.56,0:31:07.89,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.60,0:31:12.19,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to draw your\Nweapon on your superior?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.80,0:31:17.17,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Continental, I will not\Nforgive a thug like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.72,0:31:31.15,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,This incident was taken\Ncare of secretly...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.45,0:31:34.01,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Headquarters\Nwill never find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.60,0:31:42.03,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,And a couple of days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.33,0:31:45.39,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...Leonard was transferred\Nto fight at the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.03,0:32:13.09,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I have so many memories from\Nthis knife, good and bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.26,0:32:14.73,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I want you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.87,0:32:22.24,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.15,0:32:32.34,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.19,0:33:21.43,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Leonard was sent to the 2nd Titan\Nrecovery project, never to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.83,0:33:24.03,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.70,0:33:27.50,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...four, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.67,0:33:30.00,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.27,0:33:31.54,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.71,0:34:10.94,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Bail out of the mother ship immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.68,0:34:15.98,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,We will rendezvous at the\Ncoordinates 2-7, Mark 135.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.02,0:34:56.42,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy ahead! Destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.43,0:35:40.53,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Alpha 1, Beta 3, go around the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.67,0:35:42.50,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger! Alpha 1,\Nturning left...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.60,0:36:08.43,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Leonard!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.23,0:36:10.93,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.90,0:36:17.93,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd never force anyone to\Ndo what they don't want to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.01,0:36:21.98,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.65,0:36:28.61,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,I know when you look at me, you're\Nthinking of your brother, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.12,0:36:37.12,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,You are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.83,0:36:46.89,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,My last wish in this world\Nis to spend a night with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.86,0:37:16.46,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.30,0:37:22.24,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.78,0:38:43.18,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.39,0:38:46.75,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you see me in the battlefield, and if I\Nbecome one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.76,0:38:53.22,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...I want you to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.99,0:39:18.28,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Leonard! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.39,0:39:51.01,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Leonard...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.79,0:39:58.78,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.51,0:40:19.57,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Leonard, it's a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.89,0:40:59.22,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Leonard!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.95,0:42:07.55,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,2199 AD, March 15, on the surface\Nof Jupiter's satellite, Ganymede...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.62,0:42:11.32,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...The Earth Defence Force won against\Nthe Apocalypse for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.10,0:44:03.00,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't believe we would\Nfind such a thing on Mars.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.17,0:44:07.58,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it has something\Nto do with their power.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.91,0:44:12.35,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,That mysterious transmission we\Nreceived from planet Barnard...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.48,0:44:14.68,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,...mentioned something about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.68,0:44:20.68,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,So we brought the tenth S.H. P here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.29,0:44:26.19,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Then surprisingly, the main computer\Nof Battleship Iron Man was activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.33,0:44:28.23,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Battleship Iron Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.00,0:44:30.02,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.13,0:44:33.90,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks so strange\Nthat's the nickname we gave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.50,0:44:37.20,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,We are reaching the bottom floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.37,0:44:40.10,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,Please remain seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.39,0:45:08.03,Z-X,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be continued...{\i}
